<segment id="1" parent="1001" relname="preparation">3. Transmission Schemes</segment>
<segment id="2" parent="1002" relname="preparation">In this section , a conventional non-jamming scheme and two source cooperative jamming schemes are presented for the considered buffer-aided relay IoT networks .</segment>
